OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDigital exams to be        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fintroduced within years -  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FAQA                        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pupils in England could sit some of    
OL,6, their GCSE and A-level exams digitally 
OL,7, within the next few years, under exam  
OL,8, board proposals.                       
OL,10,FAQA hopes that, by 2030, at least one  
OL,11,Fmajor subject will be partly sat       
OL,12,Fdigitally in England.                  
OL,14,FIt said the reading and listening parts
OL,15,Fof its GCSE Italian and Polish exams   
OL,16,Fwill be the first to be assessed this  
OL,17,Fway, from 2026, subject to approval.   
OL,19,FSuch exams will "allow young people to 
OL,20,Fuse their digital skills", it said.    
